  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.jgoodies.binding.internal.IPresentationModel<java.lang.Object>, com.jgoodies.common.bean.ObservableBean, com.jgoodies.common.bean.ObservableBean2, java.io.Serializable

    public class ProbeModel
extends com.jgoodies.binding.PresentationModel<java.lang.Object>
    Wraps the probed object in a jgoodies binding PresentationModel. The binding takes care of transmitting updates made in the GUI (i.e. a panel that shows the objects properties) to the actual object itself.
    Author:
    Nick Collier
